    </encoding>
    <source>Music source: 'The Evangelical Hymnal' 1921, Hymn 346.</source>
    <miscellaneous>
      <miscellaneous-field name="lyrics">6.For thy faithful servants Who have entered in;
For thy fearless soldiers Who have conquered sin;
For the countless legions Who have followed thee,
Heedless of the danger, On to victory,</miscellaneous-field>
    </miscellaneous>
  </identification>
